<p><strong>About this website. </strong>AmazingRibs.com is all about the science  of barbecue, grilling, and outdoor cooking, with great BBQ recipes, tips on technique, and unbiased equipment reviews. Learn how to set up your grills and smokers properly, the thermodynamics of what happens when heat hits meat, as well as hundreds of excellent tested recipes including all the classics: Baby back ribs, spareribs, pulled pork, beef brisket, burgers, chicken, smoked turkey, lamb,   steaks, barbecue sauces, spice rubs, and side dishes, with the world's best buying guide to barbecue smokers, grills,  accessories,  and thermometers, edited by <strong><a href="http://amazingribs.com/meathead/index.html">Meathead</a></strong>.</p>
